# make-clock-with-notpad
how to make clock open it on the cmd
open note pad
'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
@echo off
title clock
@mode con cols-35 lines-7
color 7
:main
cls
echo.
echo time:%time%
echo.
echo date:%date%
echo.
ping -n 2 0.0.0.0 >nul
goto main
'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
paste this code in note pad  after that save as it with  .Bat  and run the bat file
